{"tid":1598254,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係地鐵見到條仆街大陸閪 ( 有圖 )","createTime":"2019-09-27T10:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T11:39:54.000Z","uid":319196,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a6399e98c434888149bcac1b6ad9ba0b5548368c","tid":1598254,"uid":319196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:59:13.000Z","msg":"話說是咁的 小弟搭緊地鐵坐低咗 我隔離得一個空位<br />\n去到中環站 呢條pk 望住個空位衝入嚟 仲要撞到人添<br />\n屌你 冇家教我都算啦 推開人真係好仆街 <br />\n唔開po鬧你得唔得 屌你仲要一坐低 我見到佢 打電話畀<br />\n&quot;惡毒的曹總&quot; ( 殘體 ) <br />\n跟住勁L大聲 ( 我帶住AKG耳機 開到八成聲都聽到) 用普通話 同佢個疑似上頭傾電話<br />\n跟住傾咗一陣唔知點解畀佢cut線<br />\n跟住佢就咁用粗口鬧佢 再打次多比 <br />\n今次仲要再大聲啲添<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔理你係咪畀上司屌到操<br />\n但係唔該你落到嚟香港入鄉隨俗<br />\n畀返啲禮貌其他人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i50jCVL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi50jCVL.jpg&h=c1c631c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/diMZCVR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdiMZCVR.jpg&h=1eb22706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MkwiTuj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMkwiTuj.jpg&h=7a6c8a92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7421780948db1466b9887f122a6b73576a4663f","tid":1598254,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ngYECYc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FngYECYc.png&h=ef30838f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/15ByHpU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F15ByHpU.jpg&h=400e731c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7L0WFbA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7L0WFbA.jpg&h=fd3890e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d1841c74a16a3cf2dea4adfade21c5a544e0b0a","tid":1598254,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:39:54.000Z","ms